channel.description:

[code][Launcher] Initiating CPanel. [Launcher] Initing Cache... Exception in thread "main" java.io.FileNotFoundException: data\cache\main_file_c ache.dat2 (The system cannot find the path specified) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.open(Native Method) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(Unknown Source) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(Unknown Source) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:25) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:19) at com.rs.cache.Cache.init(Cache.java:19) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:68) [/code]

item.title: Error adding control panel
item.dc:creator: @iz3_legend iz3 legend
item.description:
@iz3_legend wrote:

This error occurs when you specify a path and the computer can’t follow it to find the file. Either your path is wrong or the file isn’t there.
